# AiModelDemo - Real-time Speech Recognition API
# This API uses SignalR WebSocket connections for real-time audio streaming
# 
# SignalR Hub URL: http://localhost:5000/hubs/speech
#
# Hub Methods:
# - InitializeRecognition(language: string) - Initialize speech recognition for a language (e.g., "en-us")
# - ProcessAudio(audioData: byte[]) - Send audio data chunks for transcription
# - EndUtterance() - End current utterance and get final result
#
# Hub Events (Client receives):
# - RecognitionInitialized - Confirmation that recognition is ready
# - PartialTranscription - Real-time partial transcription results
# - FinalTranscription - Final transcription when speech segment is complete
# - Error - Error messages
